{
  "total_duration": 631.888,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 8.32,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果一个成年人给动画里的小孩配音，你会觉得奇怪吗？不会。因为真实的人是一回事，角色是另一回事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 8.67,
      "end": 24.886,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Always young"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“青春常驻”。这不是一课说 35 岁老不老，而是看一个演员怎样走进角色：真实年龄、舞台角色、服装、声音和动作，可以同时存在。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 25.236,
      "end": 42.216,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把旧场景接到现在。现在你可能更熟悉电影、动画配音、学校短剧、cosplay，或者一个视频博主在短视频里演好几个角色。一个人可以真实地是自己，也可以暂时 appear as another person，呈现成另一个角色。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 42.565,
      "end": 63.197,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "actress"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是女演员。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "stage"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是舞台，演员在观众面前表演的地方。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里不是玩游戏，而是舞台剧。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "role"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是演员扮演的角色。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "costume"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是为了角色穿的服装。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 63.547,
      "end": 79.526,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Lesson 17"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的链条很清楚：真实的 Jennifer 是一位 actress；在 stage 上，她可以 take part in a play；在 play 里，她有一个 role；costume 和表演让观众相信这个 role。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 79.876,
      "end": 96.06,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有一句要先听懂："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grown up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是长大成人的人。结尾那句"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It must be terrible to be grown up!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 Jennifer 很会演、很俏皮的回答，不是真的在抱怨长大。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 96.41,
      "end": 105.97,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇故事的核心不是衣服，而是表演：Jennifer 本人不是 17 岁，但她可以在舞台上 appear as a girl of seventeen。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 106.32,
      "end": 116.136,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，我们在后台看到 Jennifer。她是主人公的 aunt，也就是姑姑或姨妈。课文第一句说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My aunt Jennifer is an actress."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 116.486,
      "end": 135.637,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公还说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She must be at least thirty-five years old."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must be"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“我很确定、我推测她一定至少 35 岁”。注意，这不是嘲笑年龄，只是在说明真实身份和角色身份有对比。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 135.987,
      "end": 144.659,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，Jennifer 走上 stage。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In spite of this, she often appears on the stage as a young girl."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 145.009,
      "end": 156.841,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In spite of this"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“尽管如此”。真实年龄是一个事实，可舞台上她仍然可以 appear as a young girl。观众看到的是角色，不是户口本。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 157.191,
      "end": 167.702,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，新 play 要开始了。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Jennifer will have to take part in a new play soon."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她很快要参加一出新的舞台剧。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 168.052,
      "end": 186.9,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "This time, she will be a girl of seventeen."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一次，她的 role 是 17 岁的女孩。为了让观众相信这个角色，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "she must appear in a bright red dress and long black stockings."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的 dress 和 stockings 是 costume，是舞台服装，不是整篇课文的重点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 187.25,
      "end": 199.746,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，故事给了一个对比。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last year in another play, she had to wear short socks and a bright, orange-coloured dress."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "去年另一个 role 又要求另一套 costume。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 200.096,
      "end": 216.344,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后，如果有人问她多大年纪，她总是回答："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Darling, it must be terrible to be grown up!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句像舞台上的机智台词：她不是认真说长大很可怕，而是在角色里轻轻一转，把问题变成了笑点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 216.693,
      "end": 226.309,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以标题"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Always young"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好玩在这里：Jennifer 可以一次又一次走进年轻角色，在舞台上“永远年轻”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 226.659,
      "end": 235.139,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文最容易误会的地方，是把它当成“年龄焦虑”或者“衣服清单”。其实它讲的是 real person 和 role 的区别。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 235.489,
      "end": 237.928,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Jennifer 真实年龄是多少？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 238.278,
      "end": 251.47,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文只说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She must be at least thirty-five years old."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也就是主人公很确定她至少 35 岁。35 岁并不老，这里只是为了和 17 岁的 role 形成对比。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 251.82,
      "end": 255.42,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那她为什么能演 17 岁的女孩？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 255.77,
      "end": 271.73,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为她是 actress。演员会用 voice、movement、costume 和 stage presence 让观众相信一个角色。就像成年人可以给动画里的小孩配音，同学也可以在 school play 里演 king、detective 或 old man。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 272.08,
      "end": 275.333,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到底是什么意思？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 275.683,
      "end": 286.142,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这篇课文里，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是舞台剧，不是玩游戏。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "take part in a new play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是参加一出新的戏剧演出。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 286.492,
      "end": 289.778,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "appear"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是出现吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 290.128,
      "end": 301.224,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以是“出现”，但在这里更像“在舞台上呈现成某个角色”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She appears on the stage as a young girl."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她在舞台上以年轻女孩的形象出现。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 301.574,
      "end": 305.45,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后那句"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Darling"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 305.799,
      "end": 317.991,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Darling"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是亲爱的，带一点温暖和舞台感。Jennifer 的回答很俏皮：别人问真实年龄，她用角色的口吻说，长大一定很可怕吧。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
