    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 394.479,
      "end": 406.759,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "stage"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "stage"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是舞台，演员站在上面表演，观众在下面看。学校礼堂里的台子可以是 school stage，剧院里的舞台可以是 theatre stage。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 407.108,
      "end": 415.756,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "stage"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里的短语是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "on the stage"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。Jennifer 不只是在房间里换衣服，她是在 stage 上让观众相信她的 role。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 416.106,
      "end": 418.762,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "bright"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bright"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 419.112,
      "end": 420.6,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "bright"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bright"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 420.95,
      "end": 435.925,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "bright"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bright"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是颜色或光很鲜明、很容易看见。比如"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bright red"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "鲜红色，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bright orange"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "鲜橘色，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a bright screen"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很亮的屏幕。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 436.275,
      "end": 448.679,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "bright"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里两次出现："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a bright red dress"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a bright, orange-coloured dress"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这些 bright colors 帮助舞台上的角色被观众看清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 449.029,
      "end": 463.624,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 不从表格开始，而从故事开始。课文里有两个很像的“必须”或“一定”：一个是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must be"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，一个是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "have to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "或"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 463.974,
      "end": 479.326,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先看："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She must be at least thirty-five years old."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里不是“她必须 35 岁”，而是“我推测她一定至少 35 岁”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must be"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里表示 strong guess，强烈推断。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 479.676,
      "end": 493.867,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再看："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Jennifer will have to take part in a new play soon."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这不是猜测，而是新 play 有这个安排，她将不得不参加演出。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will have to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是未来的外部要求。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 494.217,
      "end": 505.261,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "she had to wear short socks"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。去年那个 role 要求她穿 short socks，所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是过去的外部要求。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 505.611,
      "end": 516.686,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "she must appear in a bright red dress"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must appear"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是猜年龄，而是角色和舞台要求她这样亮相。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 517.036,
      "end": 531.988,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以这样记：如果后面是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "be at least thirty-five"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，多半是我判断；如果后面是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "take part in"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wear"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "appear in a costume"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，多半是外部要求。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 532.338,
      "end": 540.678,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "演员的真实身份和角色身份不同，所以英语会不断说：她本来是谁，她必须在舞台上呈现成谁。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 541.028,
      "end": 557.988,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的 acting and role 放进你自己的生活。想象你参加 school play，或者拍一个 short video。真实生活里你还是你；在 play 里，你可以 appear as a detective、king、robot，或者 student from the future。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 558.337,
      "end": 582.977,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "关键模板可以先听一个完整例子："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In real life, I am a student. In the play, I appear as a detective. I have to wear a dark coat. I have to speak quietly and carefully. I am not really a detective, but I play one."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "下面练习里，不用写很长，先用 word bank 把角色、服装和说话方式填出来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 583.327,
      "end": 606.818,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课就到这。下面先做 ⓪ 跟读：听课文全文 -> 听原音 -> 录一句 -> 获取反馈，把"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must be at least thirty-five"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "in spite of this"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "appears on the stage"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "take part in a new play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bright red dress"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grown up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "读顺。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 607.168,
      "end": 631.888,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "跟读之后，再做 ① 生活场景，用英语说真实的你和你扮演的 role 有什么不同；后面 ② 完形 ③ 中译英 ④ 英译中 ⑤ 默写 一条线做下来。做完以后，爸爸的邮箱里就会收到你今天的成绩。记住，真实的人是一回事，角色是另一回事；会表演的人，可以在 stage 上一次又一次变年轻。"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
